Developer Terms of Use
des:
My Career Fit is the one stop shop to search for Careers and hear directly from employers about what it's like to work for them in branded Employer Voice Ads. Don't just choose a job, choose a career with My Career Fit. 

Try it. You can say things like, "Tell me about jobs in Cambridge, Massachusetts?" or "Find me software jobs in Boulder," and the skill will play back for you the best fitting jobs to your query. 

This skill was created using Buildlingo, a Witlingo product. For more, go to: www.witlingo.com/buildlingo
